# Stray media files in root (e.g. WhatsApp images)
*.jpeg
*.jpg
*.png
*.gif
*.webp
# Note: If you intentionally commit images inside src/ or public/, those are still tracked.
# This rule only applies to the root-level loose files; to be safe we use negation below:
!public/**
!src/**

